{"tid":1265411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[旺中靚仔借AC] ［緊急！］最後兩日！飲食界嘅巴打請入！為香港盡大家嘅力！","createTime":"2019-06-29T07:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T07:31:34.000Z","uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"85f9143460cc2e17c3794f92bcb128796c42e744","tid":1265411,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借ac一用！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日嘅香港 多謝大家互相嘅扶持<br />\n令香港繼續撐落去！<br />\n<br />\n面對香港痴線嘅租金 人工 種種嘅成本<br />\n我地真係無辦法經常罷市咁支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地亦會盡我地微少嘅力量出一份力<br />\n實行做得幾多得幾多！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飲食界可以投票嘅手足 真係唔好懶！<br />\n只要你上網print一份form<br />\n填一填簡單資料 <br />\n就已經可以申請功能組別嘅選民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[URGENT] 突擊飲食界功能級別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記住啊！30嘅前要寄到份form!<br />\n寄唔切仲可以fax!<br />\n把握埋最後幾日嘅時間！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港 加油！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kDcGmi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kDcGmi.png&h=97deaf98&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}